then A19: f is (Morphism of d,a) by A15,CAT_1:def 4;
A20: ( cod p2 ) = b by A2,CAT_1:5;
then g is (Morphism of d,b) by A16,CAT_1:def 4;
then consider h being (Morphism of d,c) such that A21: (for k being (Morphism of d,c) holds ((( p1 * k ) = f & ( p2 * k ) = g) iff h = k)) by A14,A16,A20,A19,A17;
